I have a busy life where I work until late at night and don't
have time to feel lonely.

I have fewer social interactions and spend my days commuting
between work and home.
As I continued with such a lifestyle, my heart ended up breaking.

What should I do from now on... Take a leave of absence... Quit
my job... I've been thinking about various things.
I've always liked you, my childhood friend <K>.

I wonder what you, who have become distant since then, are doing
now.

I wonder if something would have changed if I had mustered up the
courage back then.
Even if I regret it now, nothing will change. Let's go home...
